# Day 1263

Posting this as a reminder to keep reading this: [https://ai-2027.com/](https://ai-2027.com/)

TL;DR: The "AI 2027" scenario sketches a fast-escalating agent era: by 2025–2027, autonomous research/coding systems (Agent-1 → Agent-5) supercharge progress, trigger a U.S.–China compute race, blur corporate–state lines, and raise misalignment risks. Public rollouts deliver massive productivity and job shocks, while safety, governance, and geopolitics struggle to keep up. Using that arc, and things I value/understand (sovereignty, open tools, Bitcoin, families, energy) here are 5 predictions for 2040: (1) personal AI stacks replace "big-box AI," more models running on local machines (2) Bitcoin rails + micropayments take off even more and become the default machine-to-machine money, (3) energy is the new compute as we get better at making chips and Bitcoin mining stabilizes grids across the world, (4) education is more parent-led with AI tutors and proof-of-work credentials becoming way more important than a piece of paper saying you have a degree, (5) parallel civic stacks (local, voluntary) thrive as legacy institutions die off and lose legitimacy.

The gist: agents get competent, then compound; institutions react slower than code.

It's my hypothesis. Humans have always been bad at understanding exponential curves and this one seems like it's taking off quite rapidly. I'm bullish and excited, but also prepared for a crazy few years ahead. Will be fascinating to watch it all play out.

![I asked an AI without an image generator to make this image and it wrote the code to make this lol. Should've asked for an image prompt, in my prompt, but this turned out to be cool so I kept it](https://miro.medium.com/1*l9Heg7MLQjannImOlAFQBQ.png)

The code for the above image.

```xml
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI 2027 Thumbnail</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;900&display=swap');

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .thumbnail {
            width: 1200px;
            height: 630px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #16213e 100%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        /* Animated background grid */
        .grid {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 50px 50px;
            animation: gridMove 20s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes gridMove {
            0% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
            100% { transform: translate(50px, 50px); }
        }

        /* Glowing orbs */
        .orb {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(1px);
        }

        .orb1 {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
            top: 10%;
            left: 80%;
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .orb2 {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
            bottom: 20%;
            left: 10%;
            animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
        }

        .orb3 {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
            top: 60%;
            right: 15%;
            animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) scale(1); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px) scale(1.1); }
        }

        /* Content container */
        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 1000px;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        /* Main title */
        .title {
            font-size: 80px;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00ffff 0%, #ff00ff 50%, #ffff00 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3);
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            animation: titleGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes titleGlow {
            0% { filter: brightness(1); }
            100% { filter: brightness(1.2); }
        }

        /* Subtitle */
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        /* Key points */
        .points {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .point {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #00ffff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.5);
            animation: pointPulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
            min-width: 180px;
        }

        .point:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
        .point:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.6s; }
        .point:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 2.4s; }
        .point:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 3.2s; }

        @keyframes pointPulse {
            0%, 100% { 
                transform: scale(1);
                box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3);
            }
            50% { 
                transform: scale(1.05);
                box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.5);
            }
        }

        /* Bottom tagline */
        .tagline {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 30px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #ffffff;
            opacity: 0.8;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* Exponential curve visualization */
        .curve {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .curve-path {
            stroke: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.2);
            stroke-width: 3;
            fill: none;
            animation: drawCurve 10s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes drawCurve {
            0% { stroke-dasharray: 0, 2000; }
            50% { stroke-dasharray: 1000, 1000; }
            100% { stroke-dasharray: 2000, 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="thumbnail">
        <!-- Animated background -->
        <div class="grid"></div>

        <!-- Glowing orbs -->
        <div class="orb orb1"></div>
        <div class="orb orb2"></div>
        <div class="orb orb3"></div>

        <!-- Exponential curve -->
        <svg class="curve" viewBox="0 0 1200 630">
            <path class="curve-path" d="M 0,600 Q 300,580 600,400 T 1200,50"/>
        </svg>

        <!-- Main content -->
        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title">AI 2027</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">The Agent Era & Beyond</div>

            <div class="points">
                <div class="point">Personal AI Stacks</div>
                <div class="point">Bitcoin Rails</div>
                <div class="point">Energy = Compute</div>
                <div class="point">AI Tutors</div>
                <div class="point">Parallel Civics</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tagline">"Agents get competent, then compound"</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

9/5/25

Conor Jay Chepenik
